data.meta_description:
Babyface Fensta 
Is the stage name for robert emanuel of the family battle, born near Brooklyn, NY he domiciles there and other territories still. 
He has been rapping, singing and producing since 2003 as a member of one of three acts the late great Ol Dirty Bastard(from the Legendary Wu Tang Clan)was producing. Dirty had 3 acts he was grooming, The Brooklyn Zu, Manchuz and the Zu Ninjaz of which Babyface Fensta was a Manchu. Babyface Fensta was featured on two albums. One was released nationally by Edel America‚Äôs first hip hop artist Buddha Monk. His album The Prophecy won an award in Africa and Babyface Fensta was on three tracks , ‚ÄúBang it in ya whip‚Äù, ‚ÄúEast Side Story‚Äù and ‚ÄúWarrior Chief.‚Äù And on the second album (produced by the late Papa Wu) ‚ÄúVisions of the Tenth Chamber‚Äù he was on the original version of the track ‚ÄúHang em High‚Äù. 
Babyface Fensta has performed and toured with Ol Dirty Bastard and Buddha Monk throughout the states and abroad. He has recorded volumes of music with artists from Switzerland, London,England, Paris, France, Guadalupe, Senegal, Africa, Slovakia, Trentin like Lady Sweety, Tiwony, Miranda Elise and Krystal Roze to name a few and other Artists from the States like Papoose, Coco Barbie, Abillyon and Wavey Porter from GS9. 
It is now time for the world to hear what Babyface Fensta has to say. His music is for the young and the mature music lovers not programmed, who are critical fans that want art from artists, well here you have it.  A three (3) volume set you need to hear if you want a breath of fresh music from a hidden voice with a message, take a listen, go ahead We dare you:)
